rows.label: qev041202_MSG0001
rows.name: Mmm. Little money grubber back again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh ho ho hurf hurf! Mumun would never abandon best
and most handsome customers![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0005
rows.name: Bah! What is Earth alien doing here?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0006
rows.name: Bold move, Earth alien! Are you so eager to die?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0007
rows.name: Wait! Waaait wait wait wait WAIT! Friend is mistaken![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0008
rows.name:
This is business associate of Mumun! Er, less associate
and more assistant. Really just lackey, to be honest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0009
rows.name:
So much heavy lifting is hard on knees, so Mumun find
poor and desperate-looking peasant to hire.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0010
rows.name:
Human friend is no match for mighty Prone, and far
too cowardly to start trouble. So maybe Prone friends
will let [ST:gender p1=him p2=her ] slide just this once? Mmmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0013
rows.name: Hmph! Still seems like more than Earth alien deserves![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0014
rows.name:
But [ST:gender p1=he p2=she ] does look pathetic. Weak. With flabby arms.
Not worth my time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0015
rows.name: But no promises once Earth-alien pet is inside![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0016
rows.name:
Friend is most benevolent! Mumun will take full
responsibility for the actions of this...er...pet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0017
rows.name: So then! Friends want the shipment inside today?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041202_MSG0018
rows.name:
Mumun eager to get this ove...er, satisfy customers,
so in we go![ST:wait ]
